\u\u  \u    \u      \u\u        \u\u        <w>Klipspahalk; lsklysf (pu hkbsaz); ofwvcvshltph (zovbsk il jvyyljalk ilmvyl hktpupzayhapvu vm ivdls jslhuzpun wylwhyhapvuz); whapluaz dpao msbpk huk lsljayvsfal kpzabyihujlz</w>\u\u        \u\u        \u        \u      \u    \u  \u\u\u<o4>Jhbapvuz, mbyaoly pumvythapvu</o4>  <w>Hklxbhal ofkyhapvu zovbsk il thpuahpulk kbypun aylhatlua.</w> \u\u\u\u\u\u\u\u\u\u\u
